title: Ranking of the most popular blogs in Norway 2019
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Number of visitors for 10 number of Months.
The Number of visitors is appeared to be the highest at Month Sophieelise and lowest at Month Martinelunde.
There is a difference of 22210.0 between the maximum Month Sophieelise and minimum Month Martinelunde.

max_summary: This bar chart has 10 columns on the x axis representing Month, and Number of visitors in each Month on the y axis.
The Number of visitors is highest at Month Sophieelise and lowest at Month Martinelunde.
Second maximum Number of visitors is found at Month Annarasmussen.
The lowest value at Month Martinelunde is 2.86x times less than the highest value at Sophieelise.
Number of visitors at Month Sophieelise is 34173.0 , second place is Annarasmussen at 33363.0, and thirdly is Isabelleeriksen at 27246.0.
Over the past 10 Months, the Number of visitors has reduced.
The average Number of visitors in all 10 Months is 22587.9.
The Number of visitors is 225879.0 if we add up values of all Months.
